
follower cluster

using infochimps wordbag api can i cluster the people i follow on twitter?

first get the peoples user ids...
$ curl -s 'http://api.twitter.com/1/friends/ids.json?id=mat_kelcey' > friends.json

then stick that into ./get_words_for_friends.rb which injects into mongo
$ ./get_words_for_friends.rb INFOCHIMPS_APIKEY

run over and cluster ppl with
$ ./cluster.rb

irb$ require 'rubygems'; require 'mongo'; mongo = Mongo::Connection.new('localhost',12300); db = mongo.db 'wordbag'
